paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted genetic variant information for the KCNH2 gene, including penetrance data.

functional_data.summary: The loss of function frameshift variant is not present in gnomAD and is predicted to be likely pathogenic by ClinVar.

variants.additional_notes: Three of four missense variants are uniformly predicted to be damaging.
key_quotes: Rare deleterious KCNH2 variants were observed in five families, including one loss of function variant and four missense variants.

extraction_metadata.notes: All relevant data for KCNH2 variants were extracted successfully.
